Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.21,0:00:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  這麼快？！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.06,0:00:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,智花選哪件？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.90,0:00:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔  選哪件好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.92,0:00:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾脆選件大膽的  誘惑一下長谷川哥哥如何
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.85,0:00:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誘…誘惑？！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.54,0:00:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢～日向選這件
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.58,0:00:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥會不會誇我呢
